styles: .fileinput-button{position:absolute;right:60px;bottom:40px;overflow:hidden;width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:12px;transform:scale(2.5);-ms-transform:scale(2.5);-moz-transform:scale(2.5);-webkit-transform:scale(2.5);-o-transform:scale(2.5);color:#0686fd}.fileinput-button input{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;opacity:0;filter:'alpha(opacity=0)'}.pic_list{border:1px solid #ddd}.pic_list ul{padding:0;list-style:none;width:100%;margin:20px 0 0 20px}.pic_list ul li{height:120px;width:110px;margin:0 0 10px 10px;float:left;overflow:hidden;align-items:center;position:relative}.pic_list ul li button{position:absolute;top:0;right:12px;width:24px;height:24px}.pic_list ul li div img{max-width:80px;max-height:100px;align-items:center;display:block;margin:auto}.image_size{width:80px;height:100px;align-items:center;margin:auto;display:block}.pic_list ul li p.filename{text-align:center;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap}.upload_button{position:absolute;right:0}.button_group{transform:scale(1.25);-ms-transform:scale(1.25);-moz-transform:scale(1.25);-webkit-transform:scale(1.25);-o-transform:scale(1.25)}.queue_list{display:block}.file_list{list-style:none;margin:0;padding:0;overflow:hidden}.file_list li{background:#e6e6e6;border-bottom:1px solid #d3d3d3;height:36px;line-height:35px;font-size:16px;position:relative}.file_list li button{float:right;top:6px;right:10px;width:20px}.file_list li p.title{padding:0 0 0 6px;margin:0 210px 0 0}.file_list li p.size{position:absolute;width:100px;top:0;right:100px}
